Package: provoc
Title: Proportions of Variants of Concern from Counts and Coverage of a list of Mutations and a Reference for Which Variants Those Mutations may Come From
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Devan", "Becker", , "D7Becker@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3796-3946")),
    person("Jeremy", "Faria"),
    person("Daner", "Yasin")
    )
Description: Given a data frame with columns counts, coverage, and mutation, along with a matrix with rows representing Variants of Concern and columns representing mutations for those variants (entries being 1 if the mutation exists, 0 otherwise), this package provides an method to estimate the proportions of each variant of concern.
